Quickstrike:








"He is," Quickstrike said, pointing to the drone to the side of him, 
answering Dark One's question. He turned his head to it to make sure. He 
stilll felt left out of this. "Megatron?"

He suddenly paused, feeling a comm-link come through him. He put on odd 
looking hand up with eight long fingers, asking privacy from the others. He 
replied to him. "Silverstryke, that you? Where were ya?"
